F5 Digital built the Red Button APP | Emergency & Safety App as a Free app. 
This SERVICE is provided by Red Button at no cost and is intended for use as is.
This page is used to inform visitors regarding our policies with the collection, use, and disclosure of Personal Information if anyone decided to use our Service.
If you choose to use our Service, then you agree to the collection and use of information in relation to this policy. 

**Information Collection and Use**
For a better experience, while using our Service, you are required to provide the app with certain personally identifiable information, like your mobile number, name and CNIC etc.
including PERMISSION REQUIRED TO SEND SMS and PERMISSION REQUIRED TO ACCESS YOUR CURRENT LOCATION. In Future we will be adding some other permisions that can capture your picture from front and back camera and can record your audio. In future this APP will access your files to get those audio and images to know whats happend to you in that emergency moment.
The app requires permission for sending SMS to alert your emergency contacts by sending SMS when you are in an emergency. 
The app requires permission to access your current location in order to send your current location to the emergency contacts when you are in an emergency. 
The information that the app requests will be used for marketing purpose to show you some ads and other informations by our partners and Sponcers.
Link to privacy policy of third party service providers used by the app
•	Google Play Services

**Cookies**
Cookies are files with a small amount of data that are commonly used as anonymous unique identifiers. These are sent to your browser from the websites that you visit and are stored on your device's internal memory.
This Service does not use these “cookies”.

**Security**
We value your trust in providing the app with your Personal Information, thus we are striving to use commercially acceptable means of protecting it. Since the information that you provide to this app is stored locally on your device as well as on our secured servers, it is not accessible by anyone. This app ensures you maximum security of your information that it uses but is not responsible for any breach/theft of your Personal Information caused by any other application on your device or by any kind of cyber-attack on your device or on our servers.

**Links to Other Sites**
This Service contains a link to google play store in order to review this app. If you click on this link, you will be directed to the site. Note that this external site is not operated by Us. Therefore, We strongly advise you to review the Privacy Policy of this website. We have no control over and assume no responsibility for the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-party sites or services.

**Children’s Privacy**
These Services do not address anyone under the age of 13.

**Changes to This Privacy Policy**
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. I will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.
This policy is effective as of 1 November 2021
